684
01:02:25,360 --> 01:02:30,000
"So there's no position for you?" asked 
Clive, but he could see the answer coming. 

685
01:02:30,800 --> 01:02:34,400
"Right," said Eddie.
"They're making you redundant, then?" 

686
01:02:35,280 --> 01:02:38,720
"No."
Clive was confused,  

687
01:02:38,720 --> 01:02:42,880
and Eddie could not bring himself to 
say any more. So Lynn continued for him.  

688
01:02:43,680 --> 01:02:47,840
"They fired him," she said.
