695
01:03:21,680 --> 01:03:26,400
"You're very hands-on. The other day he 
said you were too hands-on, didn't he?" 

696
01:03:26,960 --> 01:03:30,000
"Exactly," said Eddie.
"And in what way are you  

697
01:03:30,000 --> 01:03:35,600
negative? You are more enthusiastic and positive 
