01:04:25,360 --> 01:04:32,640
Only a selfish need to justify themselves."
"They can't do this, surely?" Lynn asked Clive. 

708
01:04:33,200 --> 01:04:37,040
"They can and they have."
"But it's unfair dismissal.  

709
01:04:37,040 --> 01:04:41,760
You can take them to a tribunal."
