01:39:54,720 --> 01:40:02,320
in. Summer was over and the evenings were getting 
darker. Eddie had lost weight and his relationship  

1102
01:40:02,320 --> 01:40:08,320
with Lynn was in a bad way. Either they argued 
over most things or they didn't speak at all. 

1103
01:40:10,160 --> 01:40:15,760
One Thursday afternoon Lynn came in from work 
and Eddie was sitting in his armchair as usual,  

