She was always upset these days. He decided 
to shout out the rest of his commentary  

1117
01:41:25,840 --> 01:41:31,040
so that Lynn could hear him in the kitchen.
"And now their wives are complaining that  

1118
01:41:31,040 --> 01:41:36,000
the men are obsessed with arguing with each 
other. They've been fighting over the dog for  

