1120
01:41:42,800 --> 01:41:45,840
"What?" he shouted.
"Nothing." 

1121
01:41:46,880 --> 01:41:53,680
"No, go on," he shouted. "What did you say?"
"Nothing. Go back to your show. It sounds  

1122
01:41:53,680 --> 01:41:59,840
fascinating," she said. Eddie got up 
and went to see her. "What's wrong?" 

1123
01:42:00,480 --> 01:42:04,960
Lynn ignored him and started putting 
shopping away in cupboards and in the fridge. 

1124
01:42:06,560 --> 01:42:13,160
"What's wrong?" he asked again.
This time she stopped and looked at Eddie. "Erm,  

1125
01:42:13,840 --> 01:42:19,040
well, let me see. I get up in the morning 
and go to work while you sit and watch telly.  

1126
01:42:19,680 --> 01:42:25,280
I come in from work, and you're still sitting and 
