1127
01:42:25,280 --> 01:42:31,200
I do the cooking, I get no help. I try to talk to 
you, and I get nothing. You used to have breakfast  

1128
01:42:31,200 --> 01:42:35,920
with me in the mornings, and now you don't get 
up at all! We never go out. Our friends don't  

1129
01:42:35,920 --> 01:42:41,360
call us. The house is a mess, and you're here 
