1131
01:42:45,200 --> 01:42:51,440
"... and I don't hear anything positive from 
you about anything. Anything! I'm sick of it." 

1132
01:42:53,200 --> 01:42:58,080
There was a pause after she stopped.
"Bad day then?" he said. 

1133
01:42:58,080 --> 01:43:03,600
"It's not funny, Eddie. I worry so 
much about you, your job situation,  

1134
01:43:03,600 --> 01:43:08,240
money - and then I go into work and I have at 
least twenty - five kids in my class all day.  

1135
01:43:08,960 --> 01:43:12,400
I try to keep them under control 
