1144
01:44:00,560 --> 01:44:03,840
"Angela's? That's two hours 
away. When will you be back?" 

1145
01:44:04,880 --> 01:44:07,280
"Saturday."
"Saturday?" 

1146
01:44:08,000 --> 01:44:12,320
