01:48:23,760 --> 01:48:31,680
having a lie-in, I suppose. Who knows? Who cares?"
At this point Jen looked across and saw Eddie and  

1198
01:48:31,680 --> 01:48:37,280
Lynn. She pointed at them and got up to come 
over. The two men in uniform accompanied her. 

1199
01:48:38,080 --> 01:48:45,200
"Hello, Jen," said Lynn. "Is something wrong?"
"It's Dominic. He's missing. He never came  

