01:50:18,240 --> 01:50:20,880
"And did you talk to him about 
it when you saw him later?" 

1218
01:50:22,080 --> 01:50:27,680
"He didn't really remember me, and it was almost 
twenty years ago. I don't blame him. Anyway,  

1219
01:50:27,680 --> 01:50:31,760
