01:51:12,960 --> 01:51:18,160
The Parvina returned to Barbados, where the 
cruise was delayed and an official search began.  

1228
01:51:19,120 --> 01:51:22,880
Eddie saw helicopters come and 
go, and he saw police coming and  

1229
01:51:22,880 --> 01:51:28,880
going at the harbour. There was even a TV crew.
